dict.string: Wi-Fi Logs included in this report may contain personal information about your Wi-Fi connections, including transferred content and nearby Wi-Fi router hardware addresses. It may also contain Bluetooth logs that include sensitive data like phone call history, shared notification content, paired Bluetooth device names, and recently connected or nearby devices. If you're concerned about the included information, you can go back to review or remove it.

WLAN Logs included in this report may contain personal information about your WLAN connections, including transferred content and nearby WLAN router hardware addresses.
